  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA51">
<l>kuḻalār ciṟupuṟattuk kōlvaḷaiyaip pākat</l>
<l>teḻilāka vaittēka vēṇṭā - kaḻalārppap</l>
<l>pēriravi līmap peruṅkāṭṭil pēyōṭu</l>
<l>māraḻalvāy nīyāṭu maṅku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For her with curls on the small of [her] back, putting beautiful bangles</l>
<l>gracefully on one side, it is not necessary to go to where you are dancing</l>
<l>on the rare fire together with demonesses, in the great cremation ground</l>
<l>with pyres during the great night, while [your] anklets jangle.</l>
<l></l>
<l>b</l>
<l>Without having to go there, having put for beauty in one part [her with]</l>
<l>beautiful bangles, the small of [her] back full of curls,</l>
<l>you are dancing ...</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
